articles.title: Coronavirus outbreak: New travel U.S. restrictions go into effect
articles.description: The U.S. is now shut to most foreigners who have recently traveled to China amid the outbreak of the deadly coronavirus. A ninth case has been confirmed in the U.S., while Americans in Wuhan anxiously await evacuation.
